Hello everyone
:eco: :eco: :eco: 💯 💯 💯 :eco: :eco: :eco: :eco: :eco_100: :eco_100: :eco_100: 
I present to your attention a combined cosplay
of two characters in the style of Eco (Freddie Mercury and Borat)
🔥 🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥

The preparation for the shooting of the video was adventurous.
Special paint and fabric were purchased to make the flag.
The flag was drawn for 5-6 hours at night.His mother was supposed to deliver 
him to the filming location, but she accidentally left him in the subway. We spent 2 hours trying to find him in the metro, attracted metro employees, but could not find him.
We were very upset, but decided to make a new flag. We went to the market for fabric and paints. 
We spent another day on this, walked 32,000 steps.

We were very tired, but it was a pleasant fatigue, as the mission to find fabric and paint was completed.
Then we started drawing the flag again, also at night, and it took at least 3 hours.
By the morning of filming, the flag was ready.
The size of the flag has become even larger-2.5 m

According to the idea of the ECO flag, it was supposed to be a cape of Freddie Mercury, this is the only thing that somehow covered him from prying eyes.It was not easy to combine the image 
of Freddie and Borat, to be honest, I was very shy. There were people around, surprisingly 
they supported and spoke a cool image. Although I was worried that I had attracted a lot of attention.

But I decided to bring the idea to the end, so that it did not become and gave it all to the maximum.It turned out or not, you can judge.I really hope for your support.

Enjoy your viewing.
